"title": "5818: contempt",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5818: contempt",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An attitude of scorn and derision. Examples are given of the way in which a rebellious and fallen world treats its creator with contempt.</p>\n<h2>Contempt of some people for others</h2>\n<h3>Eliab for David</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:28\">1SA 17:28</a></p>\n<h3>Nabal for David</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:10-1Sam25:11\">1SA 25:10–25:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:14\">1SA 25:14</a></p>\n<h3>King Hanun for David's men</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:4-2Sam10:5\">2SA 10:4–10:5</a></p>\n<h3>Sanballat, Geshem and Tobiah for Nehemiah's men</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:19\">NEH 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:3\">NEH 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>Contempt for parents</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:5\">PRO 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:20\">PRO 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:22\">PRO 23:22</a></p>\n<h2>Contempt from the godless</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:10\">JOB 16:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:18\">PSA 31:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:18\">JOB 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:1\">JOB 30:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:21\">PSA 35:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:10\">PSA 42:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:19-Ps69:20\">PSA 69:19–69:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:22\">PSA 119:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:9-Isa28:10\">ISA 28:9–28:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:14\">ISA 28:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:7\">JER 20:7</a></p>\n<h2>God's contempt for the godless</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:4\">PSA 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:21\">JOB 12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:26\">PRO 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah3:6\">NAM 3:6</a></p>\n<h2>God will bring contempt on his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:16\">JER 18:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:9\">JER 25:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:18\">JER 25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:4\">EZK 22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:16\">DAN 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:16\">MIC 6:16</a></p>\n<h2>Human contempt for God</h2>\n<h3>For God himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:11\">NUM 14:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:23\">NUM 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:30\">NUM 16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1\">PSA 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:11\">PSA 73:11</a></p>\n<h3>For his law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:10\">PSA 78:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev22:9\">LEV 22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:9\">ISA 30:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:6\">HOS 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:9\">MRK 7:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:3\">MAT 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:28\">HEB 10:28</a></p>\n<h3>For his prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:16\">2CH 36:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:12-Amos7:13\">AMO 7:12–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:12\">MAT 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>For his works</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:10\">ZEC 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:5\">HAB 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:41\">ACT 13:41</a></p>\n<h3>For his day</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:15-Neh13:21\">NEH 13:15–13:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:5\">AMO 8:5</a></p>\n<h3>For his worship and service</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:6-Mal1:8\">MAL 1:6–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:12-Mal1:13\">MAL 1:12–1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:11\">MAL 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:8-Mal3:9\">MAL 3:8–3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:14\">MAL 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>For his gospel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:6\">MAT 7:6</a></p>\n<h3>For his kindness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">ROM 2:4</a></p>\n<h3>For his authority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10\">2PE 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>For his patience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:3-2Pet3:4\">2PE 3:3–3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as the object of contempt</h2>\n<h3>Anticipated in prophecy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:6-Ps22:8\">PSA 22:6–22:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:43\">MAT 27:43</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:19-Ps69:21\">PSA 69:19–69:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3\">ISA 53:3</a></p>\n<h3>During his earthly ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54-Matt13:57\">MAT 13:54–13:57</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:1-Mark6:4\">MRK 6:1–6:4</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:24\">MAT 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:14\">LUK 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:34\">JHN 9:34</a></p>\n<h3>While on the cross</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:39\">MAT 27:39</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:29\">MRK 15:29</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:32\">MRK 15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:39\">LUK 23:39</a></p>\n<h2>Contempt will be punished</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:26\">PRO 1:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:34\">PRO 3:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:29\">PRO 19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:10\">PRO 22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:3-Ezek25:7\">EZK 25:3–25:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:2-Ezek36:5\">EZK 36:2–36:5</a></p>\n<h2>Final punishment is contempt</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a></p>",
